/*!
 * Original code by Chakra UI
 * MIT Licensed, Copyright (c) 2019 Segun Adebayo.
 *
 * Credits to the Chakra UI team:
 * https://github.com/chakra-ui/chakra-ui/blob/main/packages/color-mode/src/color-mode-context.ts
